CẤU HÌNH HTTPS CHO TOMCAT 10 (Yêu cầu sử dụng java 11 hoặc hơn để tương thức với việc cài đặt HTTPS trên tomcat 10)
Bước 1:
Vào command prompt gõ lệnh:
cd để di chuyển tới folder tomcat 10
ví dụ: cd /d D:\Online_Movie_Booking_Ticket\apache-tomcat-10.0.27 
Bước 2:
Gõ lệnh: 
keytool -genkeypair -alias tomcat -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -keystore conf\keystore.jks -validity 3650
để tạo ra một keystore.jks với các thông tin:
Keystore password	changeit
Re-enter	changeit
First and last name	localhost
Organizational unit	IT
Organization	MyApp
City	Hanoi
State	HN
Country code	VN
Correct?	yes
sau đó sẽ có một file keystore.jks được tạo trong conf
Bước 3:
Stop tomcat server nếu đang chạy
vào file server.xml trong conf sử dụng ctrl F gõ 8443 để đi đến đoạn mã được comment như sau:
<Connector port="8443" protocol="org.apache.coyote.http11.Http11NioProtocol" maxThreads="150" SSLEnabled="true">
<UpgradeProtocol className="org.apache.coyote.http2.Http2Protocol"/>
<SSLHostConfig>
<Certificate certificateKeystoreFile="conf/keystore.jks"/>
</SSLHostConfig>
</Connector>

sau đó thêm  certificateKeystorePassword="changeit" type="RSA" vào như sau:
<Connector port="8443" protocol="org.apache.coyote.http11.Http11NioProtocol" maxThreads="150" SSLEnabled="true">
<UpgradeProtocol className="org.apache.coyote.http2.Http2Protocol"/>
<SSLHostConfig>
<Certificate certificateKeystoreFile="conf/keystore.jks" certificateKeystorePassword="changeit" type="RSA"/>
</SSLHostConfig>
</Connector>
lưu lại và start tomcat cat server
Lúc này tomcat đã được cấu hình HTTPS 